flowchart LR
    RAW[Raw CSV Files] --> PREP[Cleaning and Feature Engineering]
    PREP --> CURATED[Curated Datasets]
    CURATED --> TRAIN[Training Pipeline]
    TRAIN --> MODELS[Saved Model Artifacts]
    CURATED --> KNOW[Knowledge Preparation]
    KNOW --> EMB[Azure Embeddings]
    EMB --> STORE[Local JSON Vector Store]
    MODELS --> API[FastAPI Backend]
    STORE --> API
    API --> AGENTS[Support, Sales, Analytics Agents]
    API --> LOGS[(MongoDB)]
    API --> AZURE[Azure App Service]
    CURATED --> FABRIC[Microsoft Fabric]
    FABRIC --> SEM[Semantic Model]
    SEM --> PBI[Power BI Report]
